        &sk LSHFT &kp Z     &kp X    &kp C    &kp V       &kp B            &none    &none     &kp HOME &none &none &kp LGUI        &none     &none     &kp N     &kp M    &kp COMMA       &kp DOT   &kp FSLH &sk RSHFT
        &mo 2     &kp GRAVE &none    &kp LEFT &kp RIGHT                    &kp BSPC &kp TAB   &kp LC            &mt LGUI           &kp ENTER &kp SPACE &kp DOWN  &kp UP   &kp LBKT        &kp RBKT  &mo 2
