        &kp LSHFT &kp Z     &kp X    &kp C    &kp D      &kp V              &none    &none         &kp HOME &none &none   &kp LGUI  &none     &none     &kp K    &kp H    &kp COMMA &kp DOT   &kp FSLH &kp RSHFT
